{"tid":1478094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]澳洲嘅手足，我有幾個提議","createTime":"2019-08-16T11:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T14:13:50.000Z","uid":144626,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"45ebb5f3cee238c99ea8c8344a39bc50f7b55378","tid":1478094,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:04:21.000Z","msg":"首先，辛苦你地千里之外仍為香港奔走<br />\n更加要忍受中國領事館同埋留學生滋擾<br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔係澳洲留學，但都係外國留過學<br />\n見識過當地支那人嘅醜惡同霸道<br />\n對於呢樣野，我有幾個意見<br />\n<br />\n第一，固然係繼續原有訴求，注意安全<br />\n第二，認住搞事支那人，起底同幫佢地精忠報國<br />\n<br />\n<strong>第三最重要，對準滯澳支那人，俾壓力澳洲政府，要求收緊支那移民同留學相關簽證，因為呢段時間嘅證據足以睇到中國留學生對當地居民尤其香港人造成人身威脅，更加係對國家安全有威脅，要求澳洲政府切實執行反外國勢力干預法案，調查有關中國留學生組織同領事館關係，如果屬實應將有關人士遞解出境</strong><br />\n<br />\n祝各位平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國留學撚上"},{"pid":"3f7fef8d487e1861a4087c74a3e843fa036a41d5","tid":1478094,"uid":269686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b8e71ef6d496ea56f707723f97a026f396b7c9","tid":1478094,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:06:24.000Z","msg":"[假架d奶] 守護動物同民賤聯fd底<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1477780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1477780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88d23e35af375ee843c194f4803e33c50da18f13","tid":1478094,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9226708df893db7a5522dac8f959a7ced0b7b316","tid":1478094,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:10:00.00